data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. MUST SEE!! LOCATION LOCATION! NO HOA! Beautiful renovated home just minutes from major shopping centers and major roads like the FL Turnpike and Osceola Pkwy. Freshly painted! The house will welcome you with a living room/hall with a large open space for the enjoyment of your family and friends. It has insulated windows with energy efficiency (2021), metal roof and air conditioning were replaced (2021) making this property energy-efficient. New piping recently (2023). Also the garage was converted into a spacious Bonus Room!! Spacious entrance with enough parking space and a nice patio that characterizes it. This beautiful single-family residence feels cozy and offers a relaxed Florida lifestyle. The back porch has plenty of space to enjoy morning coffee and relaxed evenings. Large fenced backyard with shed.  Don't miss this great opportunity!!
